{"tid":990391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求教］新工返左26日工，離職即走要扣錢？","createTime":"2019-01-21T14:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T14:22:49.000Z","uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5ae12cb5f805293d0afe8e8734c97b056e6dfe","tid":990391,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟經朋友介紹 入左間公司做<br />\n<br />\n由上個月27號第一日返工 即12月27日第一日返工，<br />\n<br />\n至 今日1月21日 遞信告知老細離職。<br />\n<br />\n返平日1-5 ，放紅日<br />\n<br />\n計埋紅日假共26日。<br />\n<br />\n告知老細時，佢問我幾時入職，我話上個月27號，<br />\n佢望一望計計，唔夠一個月。<br />\n<br />\n同我講要7日通知期，話我離職日係28號。<br />\n問番我點解唔7日前通知佢，話佢都需要時間搵人，<br />\n當佢話我last day 28號時 ，<br />\n有反問佢點解唔夠一個月都要7日通知？ <br />\n佢答勞工處法例係咁寫<br />\n<br />\n佢話即我走就扣7日錢，但我堅決話即走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其間佢有chok我係咪搵到新工、人事問題之類。<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家點解我未夠一個月都要7日通知期？<br />\n無簽過contract <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 無簽任何contact , 入職時無講過細節上既野，連al 都無講過，只係填左張入職form。<br />\n<br />\n因為朋友介紹，只係見過一次面之後再電話講過salary，記得過左probation 會再加人工，就入左去做。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YG1u9b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYG1u9b7.png&h=0802c186&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"386b161b7e4e4050a748672201b8f6a4a6d22544","tid":990391,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"無約嘅ft<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家即刻唔撈佢都吹你唔漲<br />\n不過佢唔出糧你都吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd65859726c7ffd6b4b1ef76ef9fc0f63426ec28","tid":990391,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"386b161b7e4e4050a748672201b8f6a4a6d22544","tid":990391,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"無約嘅ft<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家即刻唔撈佢都吹你唔漲<br />\n不過佢唔出糧你都吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"唔啦係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0221d9bb102c3a6132bff4eaf8586b2b7389ce8","tid":990391,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"未做夠一個月法定雙方都唔使"},{"pid":"213f58cb96179f243200eeed7df43455225128b1","tid":990391,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0221d9bb102c3a6132bff4eaf8586b2b7389ce8","tid":990391,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"未做夠一個月法定雙方都唔使"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"即係唔需要通知期可即走，佢又唔可以扣我錢？"},{"pid":"a30d29d87eb75ca2cdd2b57362e34037afc1935c","tid":990391,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd65859726c7ffd6b4b1ef76ef9fc0f63426ec28","tid":990391,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"386b161b7e4e4050a748672201b8f6a4a6d22544","tid":990391,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"無約嘅ft<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家即刻唔撈佢都吹你唔漲<br />\n不過佢唔出糧你都吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"唔啦係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:18:33.000Z","msg":"係喎<br />\n你無約<br />\n即係無證明你係試用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aca72fee57a6b9591b809b2620612ac60cb4b2d","tid":990391,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213f58cb9617